            :name (n / name~0
                :op1 "Mike"~0
                :op2 "Johnson"~0)

                :polarity -~3
                :time (i / initial~4)))
        :ARG1 (h / have-org-role-91~9
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (g2 / government-organization~8
                :name (n2 / name~8
                    :op1 "House"~8))
            :ARG2 (s2 / speaker~9))
        :manner (v / vote-01~12
            :ARG2 (m / majority~11)))
    :snt2 (f / face-01~16
        :ARG0 (h2 / he~14)
        :ARG1 (c / challenge-01~18
            :ARG2 (a / avoid-01~20
                :ARG0 h2
                :ARG1 (s / shut-down-05~22
                    :ARG1 (g3 / government-organization~21
                        :ARG0-of (g / govern-01~21)))
                :time (b / by~23
                    :op1 (d / date-entity~24
                        :day 17~24
                        :month 11~24)))
            :mod (u / urgent~17))
        :time (n3 / now~15)))
